Package test

Class BankAccountTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • test.BankAccountTest

  • public class BankAccountTest
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is a test class that tests BankAccount. Each individual account type is tested as well as their interest values. A given balance is tested with each interest type to make sure that the interest calculations are correct for all account types.
    Version:
    1.0.0 February 7, 2018
    Author:
    Bailey Garner
